    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I'll take your word for it then. It's just that the tension is so high right now, and if we're blindsided by something that was clearly visible in the data, the fallout for the agency—and the diplomatic mission—will be catastrophic. Just make sure you aren't smoothing over anything too aggressively. We can't afford to be wrong on this one.",
